choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.
Breakfast: 2 slices of whole wheat toast with peanut butter and banana sliced on top, a glass of orange juice and a bowl of oats with blueberries.
Lunch: A salad made up of romaine lettuce, carrots, tomatoes, cucumbers, chicken breast and a side of hummus.
Dinner: Grilled or baked salmon fillet (or another type of fish) served over brown rice with steamed broccoli and asparagus on the side. A piece of fruit for dessert.
